14
00:00:45,070 --> 00:00:47,170
-What is DOOL? -Days Of Our Lives.
-什么是DOOL？ -《我们的日子》

15
00:00:49,210 --> 00:00:53,010
You won't believe it. My character is coming out of his coma!
你们一定不相信 我演的角色就要醒过来了

16
00:00:53,210 --> 00:00:55,150
-That's wonderful. -Wow, Joey.
-那真的是太棒了 -哇，乔伊

17
00:00:55,420 --> 00:00:59,110
And not only that. I'm getting a new brain!
不只是那个，我会有个新脑子！

18
00:01:00,220 --> 00:01:04,320
So great things are happening at work and in your personal life.
你的工作跟私生活 都有了很棒的进展

19
00:01:05,530 --> 00:01:07,090
You're getting a new brain?
你要换个新脑子？

20
00:01:07,300 --> 00:01:09,990
They're killing off one of the characters...
他们要踢走剧中一个角色…

21
00:01:10,200 --> 00:01:13,170
and her brain is being transplanted into my body.
将她的脑子移植到我的身体里

22
00:01:15,070 --> 00:01:18,510
What? A brain transplant?
什么？脑部移植手术？

23
00:01:18,770 --> 00:01:20,330
