这太可笑了

24
00:01:20,580 --> 00:01:23,770
It's ridiculous that you haven't had sex in three months.
可笑的是你三个半月没有做过爱

25
00:01:28,520 --> 00:01:32,280
It's winter. There are fewer people on the street.
现在是冬天，街上的人少了很多

26
00:01:33,690 --> 00:01:34,920
Who are they killing off?
他们要踢走谁？

27
