30
00:01:43,930 --> 00:01:46,590
I don't think I've ever seen her finish a drink.
我从来没看过她喝完一杯饮料

31
00:01:46,870 --> 00:01:49,390
The way she slaps people. Wouldn't you love to?
还有她打人巴掌的样子 你不想那么做吗？

32
00:01:49,670 --> 00:01:51,160
Don't do it.
别那么做

33
00:01:52,010 --> 00:01:53,870
And she's been on the show forever.
她参与这出戏的演出很久了

34
00:01:54,080 --> 00:01:56,670
It's gonna be really hard to fill her shoes.
要代替她一定很难

35
00:01:56,850 --> 00:01:58,040
Help me out here.
你得帮帮我

36
00:01:58,310 --> 00:02:02,810
When you come out of the brain transplant...
当你做过脑部移植手术后…

37
00:02:03,050 --> 00:02:05,920
you are going to be her?
你要变成她？

38
00:02:06,150 --> 00:02:09,060
Yes, but in Drake Ramoray's body.
对，她被困在德瑞克的身体里

39
00:02:12,090 --> 00:02:15,590
Why is this so hard for you to get? I thought you were a scientist.
