如果他打电话来找手机 我接了电话…

51
00:03:32,810 --> 00:03:36,170
and we start talking and we fell in love?
我们开始聊天，之后坠入爱河呢？

52
00:03:36,380 --> 00:03:38,540
Would that be a great story?
那是个很棒的故事吧？

53
00:03:38,810 --> 00:03:41,610
Kind of like a fairy tale for the digital age.
就像是数位时代的童话故事

54
00:03:42,380 --> 00:03:44,510
That does sound great. I'm getting the phone.
那听起来很棒，我要去拿手机

55
00:03:44,790 --> 00:03:48,050
What? Wait. Why do you get the story?
什么？等一下 为什么你会成为故事的女主角？

56
00:03:48,290 --> 00:03:50,990
I haven't been out on a date in so long.
我已经很久没有约会了

57
00:03:51,260 --> 00:03:53,690
Phoebe, you had a date three days ago.
菲比，三天前你才约过会

58
00:03:53,960 --> 00:03:58,520
That wasn't a date. That was friends getting together and having sex.
那不是约会，那只是 朋友聚会，然后做爱

59
00:03:58,800 --> 00:04:00,890
Okay. Great. I get the phone.
好吧，我去拿手机

60
00:04:01,170 --> 00:04:04,300
No way. You just broke up with Tag a week ago.
不行，一星期前你才跟泰格分手

61
00:04:04,540 --> 00:04:09,810
Yeah, and until now, I didn't think I would love again.
对，直到现在，我才明白 我能再爱一次

62
00:04:10,810 --> 00:04:12,070
-Nice try. -Wait.
-说的好 -等一下

63
00:04:12,350 --> 00:04:15,410
How do we fairly decide who gets the phone?
我们该怎么公平地决定 谁能拿走手机呢？

64
00:04:15,680 --> 00:04:17,480
I don't know.
我不知道

65
00:04:24,430 --> 00:04:26,860
Maybe we could...
或许我们可以…

66
00:04:27,900 --> 00:04:29,230
Ah-ha! Too slow!
你动作太慢了！

67
00:04:31,530 --> 00:04:34,230
Ah-ha! Too cocky.
你太自大了

68
00:04:36,643 --> 00:04:38,167
（银杯片厂）

69
00:04:38,570 --> 00:04:41,010
I'm dating him. There's nothing you can do.
我在跟他约会，你管不了

70
00:04:41,210 --> 00:04:42,230
Yes, there is.
不，我管得了

71
00:04:42,510 --> 00:04:45,740
Are you going to kill him like you did Charles?
你打算怎么做？杀了他吗？ 就像你杀了查尔斯？

72
00:04:47,680 --> 00:04:50,450
Oh, my baby.
我的宝贝

73
00:04:54,890 --> 00:04:56,290
Cut!
卡！

74
00:05:00,500 --> 00:05:05,060
That was great. And that slap looked so real. How do you do that?
你演得太好了，刚刚那一巴掌 很逼真，你怎么办到的？

75
00:05:05,270 --> 00:05:08,930
-Oh, just years of experience. -Can I get some ice here?!
-那只是多年的经验 -快拿冰块过来给我

76
00:05:10,640 --> 00:05:13,440
I just wanted to say how wonderful I think you are.
我只想说我觉得你的演技很棒

77
00:05:13,810 --> 00:05:16,300
You're not the fan who's dying,  are you?
你该不会是那个快死掉的影迷吧？

78
00:05:17,480 --> 00:05:20,500
I'm Joey Tribbiani. We did a scene together yesterday.
我是乔伊崔比亚尼 昨天我们合拍过一场戏

79
00:05:20,750 --> 00:05:24,120
-I'm the guy in the coma. -Oh, that was a real person?
-我就是那个昏迷的人 -那是真人？

80
00:05:26,620 --> 00:05:30,520
Since I'm getting your brain when you leave the show...
因为你离开后我要移植你的脑子…

81
00:05:30,760 --> 00:05:32,620
I was wondering if..
我在想如果…

82
00:05:32,860 --> 00:05:36,350
-I'm leaving the show? -Why? Did you hear something?
-我要离开？ -为什么？你听到了什么？

83
00:05:38,000 --> 00:05:40,230
Who told you that?
是谁告诉你的？

84
00:05:40,800 --> 00:05:44,000
-One of the writers. -Was it bald or was it tall?
-编剧之一 -哪个编剧？是秃头佬还是高个子？

85
00:05:45,010 --> 00:05:48,130
You know, it doesn't matter,  because it is not true.
那不重要，因为那不是真的

86
00:05:48,380 --> 00:05:49,570
Okay.
好吧

87
00:05:49,740 --> 00:05:53,370
And if it were true, how dare you come to me and ask me for tips...
如果那是真的 你竟然敢来叫我教你…

88
00:05:53,610 --> 00:05:56,310
about a character I've played for 20 years!
该如何饰演我演了二十年的角色

89
00:06:01,560 --> 00:06:04,320
Miss Monroe.. Oh, there you go.
梦露小姐…喔，你真的那么做了

90
00:06:08,760 --> 00:06:10,060
Okay, look, I have an idea.
好吧，听着，我有个点子

91
00:06:10,300 --> 00:06:14,630
Why don't we see what kind of numbers he has on his speed dial...
我们为什么不看看 他的速拨键记录了哪些电话号码…

92
00:06:14,870 --> 00:06:19,360
and then whoever has more in common with him gets the phone.
跟他有最多共通点的人 就可以把手机拿走

93
00:06:20,040 --> 00:06:22,840
-Fine. All right. -All right.
-好吧 -好吧

94
00:06:23,180 --> 00:06:26,340
First name on the speed dial is "Mom."
速拨键的第一个名字是“妈妈”

95
00:06:26,580 --> 00:06:29,380
Oh. I lost my mom to suicide.
喔，我妈妈自杀死了

96
00:06:29,880 --> 00:06:33,480
